competitions.title: USACO (USA Computing Olympiad) #1
competitions.description: A 3-day prestigious programming competition with 4 divisions. You will have 3-5 hours to complete 3 problems virtually. More information coming soon!

competitions.title: ACSL Contest (American Computer Science League) #1
competitions.description: A national competition consisting of a short answer and programming portion. You will either compete in the Intermediate or Senior division. More information coming soon!
